Cluj-Napoca Private Clinic: SABINI Medical Clinic.

What is Sabini?

SABINI is a Private Clinic from Cluj-Napoca. We can offer patients the professionalism of an exceptional medical team; over 120 doctors covering the important medical specialties in an integrated manner, ensuring the necessary investigations in well-structured departments in Zalau and Cluj-Napoca.

Medical services settled by CAS.

All persons who are insured according to the legislation in force can benefit from consultations/investigations based on the referral ticket.
